#

Savory Beef Ragu with Handmade Pasta

$30
650 kcal

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

ItalianHeartyHomemade

Description

A rich and hearty beef ragu paired with tender handmade pasta, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Beef chuck roast: 2 pounds
  • Carrots: 2, diced
  • Celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • Onion: 1 large, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Crushed tomatoes: 1 can (28 ounces)
  • Red wine: 1 cup
  • Beef broth: 2 cups
  • Fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Flour: 2 cups (for pasta)
